Package: wmctrl
Type: Package
Title: R interface to wmctrl command
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-11-25
Author: Paul Murrell
Maintainer: Paul Murrell <paul@stat.auckland.ac.nz>
Description: Provides R functions to control the windows and mouse on a
  Linux desktop (with an X Window manager that is compatible with the 
  EWMH/NetWM specification). The functions all work by making system calls 
  to the wmctrl command.
License: GPL-3
SystemRequirements: wmctrl, pidof
